# Claude Code — project config (agents/commands/hooks/skills/settings.json) is tracked;
# local state (settings.local.json, worktrees, locks) and installed skill contents stay
# local. skills-lock.json is tracked so the skill set is reproducible.
.agents/
.claude/*
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
tmp.md

